Want to bring your sticker collections and awesome gifs to the meeting? Then StampIt is your all-in-one solution. Spice up the google meet chats with this chrome extension to send various formats of content from emojis to stickers, and even create your own too, all in StampIt!

- Send exciting emojis, GIFS and stickers in Google Meet chats
- Simple and intuitive chrome extension
- Create and customize your own stickers and collections.
